{"tid":1898349,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【iBond】政府計劃今年內再次發行通脹掛鈎債券","createTime":"2020-02-26T05:05:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-21T07:54:09.000Z","uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f18278afae40c70a719eb707609e2201bb60d09a","tid":1898349,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T05:05:33.000Z","msg":"預算案公布，香港按揭證券有限公司將推出試驗計劃，透過銀行提供上限為1千萬港元，年利率分別為百分之2.75、2.85及 2.95的 10、15及20年期定息按揭貸款，計劃總貸款額為10億港元，會視乎市場反應再檢討，可讓有意置業人士有更多貸款選擇，減低面對利率波動的風險。<br />\n<br />\n退休理財方面，預算案提出，將香港年金計劃的最低投保年齡由 65歲降至60歲，香港年金公司盡快公布詳情。<br />\n<br />\n預算案表明，計劃今年內再次發行通脹掛鈎債券，並繼續發行銀色債券，兩項債券總發行額不少於 130億元，金管局稍後公布細節。另外，當局計劃在未來5年發行約660億元綠色債券。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1510858-20200226.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1510858-20200226.htm&d=RwLhzhYA7Smtfd5%2FYaS6X7VsU2rIM%2B0kfQ6zMqXKyqM%3D&h=3d398871\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1510858-20200226.htm&h=6430e7ef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1510858-20200226.htm</a>"},{"pid":"fb44298acc88abc50e0e4b2830c16df28c01e999","tid":1898349,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T05:10:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35e6915e721f42c72cb83dffa5d7b5698db52777","tid":1898349,"uid":156327,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T05:12:41.000Z","msg":"即係人民幣出力印"},{"pid":"989224dcd003dcf0d1189fc360d81bb8b99ad2b0","tid":1898349,"uid":54502,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T05:14:47.000Z","msg":"最近一期要keep3年先得600幾蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca45d8ba2ac1233a82e5e7ffb6548b6890198b27","tid":1898349,"uid":101945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T07:54:09.000Z",